{"tid":432813,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"剛果婦向反政府軍提供魚肉　被迫與二房兒子當眾行「姦刑」","createTime":"2017-10-12T00:30:35.000Z","updateTime":"2017-10-12T06:31:25.000Z","uid":53379,"like":0,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":16,"replies":[{"pid":"a22792b24eaaaa4a53a74b3cfa07894c85683e0a","tid":432813,"uid":53379,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-12T00:30:35.000Z","msg":"<strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">剛果婦向反政府軍提供魚肉　被迫與二房兒子當眾行「姦刑」</span></strong><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://fs.mingpao.com/ins/20171011/s00005/6d3a7844bd7c0d53b145f46a36c89832.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Ffs.mingpao.com%2Fins%2F20171011%2Fs00005%2F6d3a7844bd7c0d53b145f46a36c89832.jpg&h=3a5cd235&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n非洲剛果一名女子向反政府軍士兵送上魚肉作食物。反政府軍高層獲悉後，指控她違反抗戰戒律，決定處以「姦刑」，先逼她跟丈夫二房所生兒子性交，再砍下兩人頭顱曝屍兩日。<br />\n<br />\n法國世界媒體旗下「法國24」頻道近日公開一段片段，聲稱是今年4月8日在西開賽省魯波鎮拍下。數名反政府軍士兵扯着一名裸女頭髮，拖到廣場行「姦刑」。軍方下令婦人跟家中二房生下的兒子性交，事後士兵殺死並斬下兩人頭顱。現場有大批群眾圍觀，邊看邊歡呼。<br />\n<br />\n剛果事務研究員席巴蘭加（Anaclet Tshimbalanga）說，反政府軍曾下令所有士兵在抗戰期間不得大魚大肉、不許有性行為、不能洗澡，但是婦人被指在她開設的餐館中，為士兵送上魚肉，觸犯了戒律。他又說，反政府軍今年3月佔領過魯波鎮20多日，相信事件是在期間發生。<br />\n<br />\n（太陽報）<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://news.mingpao.com/ins/instantnews/web_tc/article/20171011/s00005/1507716848561\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.mingpao.com%2Fins%2Finstantnews%2Fweb_tc%2Farticle%2F20171011%2Fs00005%2F1507716848561&d=u8Nhkge%2Bqud1T9RSgK9IEZ4%2BuNhYgvPKbWZYs3KJomg%3D&h=d1d7ef82\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.mingpao.com%2Fins%2Finstantnews%2Fweb_tc%2Farticle%2F20171011%2Fs00005%2F1507716848561&h=57dda0e7\" target=\"_blank\">https://news.mingpao.com/ins/instantnews/web_tc/article/20171011/s00005/1507716848561</a>"},{"pid":"ea37c7a6667865ddf5bc64eb494e993b2c752c90","tid":432813,"uid":37735,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-12T00:35:48.000Z","msg":"不能洗澡<br />\n<br />\n班黑鳩臭到<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d075ec638a62dbe681f55726db59db91c493f72a","tid":432813,"uid":49258,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-12T00:38:18.000Z","msg":"成班生番"},{"pid":"36e24266e2acc1d33848f8896c17efb763b4c92a","tid":432813,"uid":80392,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-12T00:38:52.000Z","msg":"咁關個仔咩事？"},{"pid":"82f7419e5b4f607367bdf0f97b2f9da511eebbdc","tid":432813,"uid":124471,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-12T00:39:51.000Z","msg":"點解二房個仔要死<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4880ded40101e8bd7928c2baf39b5859168874b0","tid":432813,"uid":53379,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-12T00:46:06.000Z","msg":"生蕃國<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b076ac9c9550ac90620c0ff81415e05c6ec59c49","tid":432813,"uid":46933,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-12T00:46:09.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>點解二房個仔要死<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n生番係唔洗講道理"},{"pid":"e28ceb33f5b5c6f8068bb91e80ba50146fd82ee7","tid":432813,"uid":50740,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-12T00:55:13.000Z","msg":"俾飯你食要死刑<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"28f81396da1f3a9843e1279c47f2f81bede7db45","tid":432813,"uid":127177,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-12T01:17:55.000Z","msg":"Niga <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bc72b268bd0d076cfaf1ef3a0f67d9df58517890","tid":432813,"uid":106348,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-12T01:24:51.000Z","msg":"姦刑都俾佢地諗到 原來生番都有睇av<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkg